media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9oK","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/08\/laylat-al-qadar-seven-nights\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last seven nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLook for the Night of Decree in the last ten nights of Ramadan. If one of you is weak or unable, then do not be overcome by the remaining seven nights.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1165 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/25\/laylat-al-qadr-peaceful-calm\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Laylat al-Qadr: Night of Decree is peaceful and calm","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said regarding the Night of Decree, \u201cIt\u00a0is a calm night, neither hot nor cold, and the sun rises upon its day red and faint.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2192 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/12\/laylat-al-qadr-dua-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Laylat al-Qadr: Dua on Night of Decree in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, if I know which night is the Night of Decree, what should I say during it?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, You are pardoning. You love to forgive, so forgive me.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/18\/siyam-salat-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Reward of fasting and praying in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan due to faith and seeking reward, his previous sins will be forgiven. Whoever stands in prayer during the Night of Decree due to faith and seeking reward, his previous sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/laylat-al-qadar-thousand-months\/","url_meta":{"origin":36130,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadar better than a thousand months","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said when the month of Ramadan began, \u201cVerily, this month has presented itself to you. There is a night within it that is better than a thousand months. Whoever is deprived of it has been deprived\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"